items.name: Snapshots of Youth: 1980s Tokyo
items.description: This model has been trained on photographs of young adults taken in Tokyo during the 1980s. The photos were taken on 35mm film using consumer cameras. This results in a model that creates candid compositions, often with bright flash lighting. The distinctive tones of 35mm film and tungsten lighting are recreated, along with the bold fashions of young Eighties Japan.

items.name: Movie Style Backgrounds
items.description:
Introducing Movie Style Backgrounds Model: An AI Model for Generating Cinematic Backgrounds

Movie Style Backgrounds Model is trained to generate immersive and cinematic backgrounds inspired by various movie styles. With training spanning 10 epochs and 2520 steps, this model has been specifically developed using movie style backgrounds obtained from the results of StableDiffusionXL, resulting in a rich collection of visually captivating and atmospheric scenes.

Introducing the "PrefixMix" Model: Redefining Generative Possibilities


Follow me:


Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/LaraFoxes

Ko-Fi: https://ko-fi.com/vidsamonboban

Hugging face: https://huggingface.co/samonboban

Coffee: https://www.buymeacoffee.com/dashboard

Twitter: https://twitter.com/samonboban

Prepare to be captivated by the innovative power of the "PrefixMix" model. This groundbreaking creation transcends traditional generative AI, revolutionising the creative landscape with its unique approach. Immerse yourself in the beauty of its output and allow us to take you on a captivating journey of exploration.

Example of prompt:

Unparalleled excellence, a true work of art, exhibiting a photorealistic quality (scale:1.4), featuring a captivating young woman with a gentle smile. She is portrayed from the waist up, adorned in a shirt adorned with collars. The scene is bathed in dramatic lighting, casting captivating shadows, and emphasizing the subject's features from a lower angle, creating a compelling visual impact.

Negative prompt: nsfw, ng_deepnegative_v1_75t,badhandv4, (worst quality:2), (low quality:2), (normal quality:2), lowres,watermark, monochrome

Steps: 30, Sampler: Euler a, CFG scale: 7, Seed: 2051385074, Size: 512x768, Model: PrefixMix, Clip skip: 2, ENSD: 31337, CFG Rescale phi: 0, Version: v1.4.0-RC-14-gdbc88c96

Used embeddings: ng_deepnegative_v1_75t [1a3e]

A Fusion of Prefixes, An Unforgettable Blend

The Symphony of Coefficients:

Central to the "PrefixMix" model's success lies the delicate harmony of coefficients. Like skilled conductors, these coefficients blend seamlessly, infusing each generative aspect with a touch of brilliance. Through their precise orchestration, "PrefixMix" transforms ordinary prompts into extraordinary works of art, pushing the boundaries of creative expression.

Unveiling the Vision:

The genesis of the "PrefixMix" model arose from a vision that sought to redefine the art of generative AI. Fuelled by a profound desire to unlock new creative frontiers, this model was meticulously crafted. It represents the culmination of a relentless pursuit to fuse the strengths of exceptional models into a unified force of artistic ingenuity.

Ignite Your Creative Spark:

With the "PrefixMix" model as your creative companion, the possibilities are boundless. Unleash your imagination, experiment with enthralling prompts, and watch in awe as your visions materialize into stunning reality. Whether you seek to craft awe-inspiring visual art, innovate in the realm of digital design, or weave compelling narratives, "PrefixMix" is here to propel your creative endeavors to new heights.

Embrace a new era of generative exploration. Step into the world of "PrefixMix," where artistic prowess converges with technological brilliance. Join us on this exhilarating journey as we redefine the very essence of creative expression.

Drawing inspiration from the very essence of its name, "PrefixMix" marries the artistry of various prefix models with unparalleled finesse. It masterfully intertwines the creative genius of HassanBlend 1.5.1.2 by sdhassan, the imaginative wonders of Uber Realistic Porn Merge (URPM) by saftle, the photorealistic brilliance of Protogen x3.4 and x5.3 by darkstorm2150, the captivating artistry of Art & Eros (aEros) + RealEldenApocalypse by aine_captain, the dreamlike aesthetics of Dreamlike Photoreal 2.0 by sviasem, the exceptional capabilities of HASDX by bestjammer, the ethereal enchantment of Analog Diffusion by wavymulder, the mesmerizing WoopWoop-Photo by zoidbb, and the visionary concepts behind AbsoluteReality by Lykon, CyberRealistic by Cyberdelia, and Analog Madness by CornmeisterNL.

I really liked "Ultra kaijuu gijinka keikaku". This is a content in which the monsters(kaijuu) of the Ultraman series are personified as cute girls. I have always been familiar with the Ultraman series as a child (I did not watch the TV series in real time, but it was my parents' influence), and I was hoping that it would pick up steam in the future...

However, this content has been inactive since around 2019 already, due to some problems with figure sales, including an abrupt halt to sales...

I love Tsuburaya Productions. Please I sincerely hope they will resume media development of this content again.

Aguila is one of the kaijuu in Ultra Seven and one of the Capsule Monsters that serve Ultra Seven.

Aguila has a single horn on its forehead and its special move is the 'Dino Dash', in which it rushes forward and thrusts the horn into the enemy.

items.name: Multiple penises
items.description:
LoRA trained to generate multiple penises, surrounding a character or in a gangbang. Suggested by another user.

Please rate and leave a like if you enjoyed it! And be sure to follow to check out the upcoming models.

Trigger word: multiple penises, multiple boys

Other useful tags: surrounded, too many, gangbang

Use any combination of the tags above to modify the effect, and increase their weight according to your preference. See my example prompts in the image gallery.

If the lora's weight or the tags weight is over 1.0 then you might start seeing some censoring, due to large portion of the dataset having some sort of censor. To counter this you can add in the negative prompt (and increase weight where needed), e.g.: censored, bar censor, censoring.

Note: I trained without the trigger captions, so if it's not working in the base model you're using let me know and I'll upload a version trained with captions.

Additional info

I make these models for fun and for the challenge and release them for free for everyone to enjoy, for non-commercial use (see license). The one thing I ask of you is to provide rating and feedback! That helps me understand where I can improve and helps me stay motivated to produce more content! I accept suggestions or requests here or on Civitai discord server.

You can also check my more polished images and upcoming models on my pixiv profile.

items.name: Catherine Bell
items.description:
A commission of @Zorglub.

Catherine Bell is a British actress and model, known for her roles in TV shows such as JAG and The Good Witch.

140-step TI trained on a dataset of 15 images with these settings. It's based on her looks of around 2010.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Building a good prompt with my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of (cathb3ll:0.99), a woman as a sexy student, closeup portrait, long straight haircut, ({yellow|white|blue|purple|green} tight long sleeve turtleneck top), at a cantina sitting bar (masterpiece:1.5) (photorealistic:1.1) (bokeh) (best quality) (detailed skin texture pores hairs:1.1) (intricate) (8k) (HDR) (wallpaper) (cinematic lighting) (sharp focus), (eyeliner), (painted lips:1.2), (earrings), (smile)"

Trained for 10 epochs with 4 repeats per image. 49 images in the dataset

Sometimes her glasses won't appear, nor her pubic hair but you can force it with tags. Use clip skip 2, 0.8 strength and highres fix with 0.5 denoise for best results. Feel free to play with the settings as needed.

Don't expect her uniform to accurately generate, most times you'll get her white shirt + bow.

items.name: Extra Faces (Ranni) | Concept LoRA
items.description:
Extra Faces (Ranni) | Concept LoRA

An additional LoRA for our Girl Ranni. Other Characters can now feel like Ranni.

Weight can go from 0.8 up to 1.3. I recommend 1. Works with almost every Style, every Character and Photorealistic Models.

Trigger Word:

ExtraFacesRanni

How to use LoRA's in auto1111:

  • Download LoRA

  • Copy the file to stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora

  • Select your LoRA and use the triggerword

  • Make sure to change the weight if needed (by default it's :1)

  • Have Fun!

items.description:
The main character from the show. This model works well in all shapes and sizes. Compatible with other TIs and LoRAs. Her bow usually is polka dot, but will adjust for other descriptions. 10k steps at a rate of .0005

Trained with NAI model
